emberhollow.revisit_text:
Emberhollow again. {if renown >= 3}People nod as you pass now — word of your deeds is getting around.{else}{if renown >= 1}A few villagers nod warily. Word travels.{else}Nobody meets your eye. Expendables aren't worth knowing.{end}{end}

{if has('ashen_crown')}[bold magenta]The crown murmurs in your pack, and every shadow in the village leans toward you.[/]{end}

Inn, blacksmith, apothecary, well — and the gates.
